<br>
Scenerio 1: (from my wizards view) My wiz is level 40. she plays with the same 6 ppl all the time(War, War, Chanter, Cleric, Shaman, Wiz) Her role as snarer/evacer/Damage Dealer is secure as long as we fighting blues.  When we were in 20's we went to Nurga and were fighting pretty much nonstop I finally gave up casting because all that happened was I got resist messages.  I would spend the night practicing conjeration, nothing else to do<br>
<br>
Now that we are over 35 we mostly fight blues so that isnt so much of an issue, But still when we have a big pull, so I burn down the first 2 or 3 as fast as I can, then I med thru the rest and the next 2 - 3 pulls after.  We are currently in Droga (at chief) and our biggest pull to date is 8,  The melees .. they get to (have to) keep fighting and Im out for the next 5 min or so.<br>
<br>
Lastly parse the damage done by either of those two warriors and compare it to mine.  They are moderately twinked, some cobalt/crusty.  Im moderately twinked but no flowing thought items (Doh!) or other things that improve my casting efficiency (rt click nukes, etc)<br>
<br>
