<br>
Seems like a proper comparison.  Now for the drastic imbalances that have caused this whole stink:<br>
<br>
Heals do not get resisted<br>
Heals are WAY more mana effecient than nukes (think Cheal and celestial elixer)<br>
Heals draw very little aggro<br>
You cannot &quot;heal&quot; mana (necros can twitch at a horrid ratio but only healers are going to get the twitch due to previously stated effeciency)<br>
melee damage is a high % of what our nukes do in the same timeframe (melee can dish out quite a lot of damage in 6 seconds) <p><b><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=68788'>Oxoxo Xoxox</a></b> Sorcerer<BR>

